Verna
Ugom/origin
‘Verna’ hem nanv ‘Varunapuri’ hea utravoilean ailam.Varunapuri mhonllear somdirache devachem xhar.Varuna mhonnllear somdiracho dev ani puri mhonllear xhar.
Verna ganvche uttor purv dishent Sal nhoi vanvta. Hea ganvant doria vell na.Eke adle mog kannye promonnem Vishnu nanvacho cholo ani Aruna nanvachi choli ekamekacho mog kortalim.Punn ganvkarani hea zodpeak jivexim marlim ani tanchi modim laslim.Oxem mantat ki Arunacho ‘Varuna’ hea fullache zhadache rupan punorzolm zalo.Haka lagun Verna hem nanv hea ganvak podlem oxem mantat.
Aruna mhonllear fantod. Fantod hi eka tajeponachem protik zavun asa.Teach bhaxen Verna ganvant kolkolte ani shitoll zori ani tollim hea ganvant shitoll ani tazem vatavoronn hadtat.Dekhun purtugezani hea ganvak tazi bhuim oxem nanv dovorlem.
Verna ganvank Verna panchayat lagu zata.Hea ganvche 16 vadeanim vantlolo asa.Verna ganvche vadeanchim nanvam oxim asat Poribhatt, Cumborda, Dignnem, Povacao, Bamborda, Senaulim, Mathol, Old Mardol, Sodovi, Ambulor,Mungrupoi,Dulape,Manzo,Dando, Ambeqim,Ambebhag.Kaim vadeanchi nanvam vadekaranche dhondea promonnem podleant oxem mantat.Cumborda vadeant khubxe khumbar ravtat.Poribhat vadeant adlea tempar pori(devlantlim kolvontam) ietaleo.Heo pori Mardolchea devllantlean Poribhatant ietaleo.
