Ganvcheo bhugolik khaxeltaeo
Verna uddegik xharak(Verna Industrial Estate) ‘ Verna’ hem nanv asa pun to vattar atam Nagoa ganvak lagu zata.Poilim Verna anik Nagoa ganv ekuch ganv also pun uprant te don ganv zale.Verna uddegik xharak sodlear ho ganvti vattar.Hanga vhodloso bazaar ani sovloteo nant.Ganvkar gorjechem saman hadpak Madgaum vetat.Verna Madgaumche uttor dishent 10 km pois asa.
Igorz,Devull,Munument
Igorz:1812 hea vorsa Povocao vadeant Holy Cross Igorz bandleli.Igorz sobit ani sundor dista .Igorje fuddem vhod moll asa.
Devull:Mardol vaddeant Mhalsa Narayani (Kalimata) he devtechem devull asa.Punn 1560 hea vorsa poilim heach zagear ek vhodd devull aslem .Jednam purtugezani hem devull modlem tednam lokani he devtek fondechea Mardol ganvant vhorun dovorli.
Dhovo khuris: 1519 vorsak Purtugez captain Rui De Melo ani tache vangdi saxti talukeant bhitor sorun Mardol devlla sorxim pavle.Thoim tannim chudtancho ek adsar koso kelo ani saxtint poilem mis hanga bhetoilem.Uprant he ghodnnukeche ugdasak ek Dhovo khuris bandlo.Poribhatt vaddeant Holy Cross Kopel anik Mungrupoi vaddeant Lume saibi nichem Kopel asa.
